{"tid":905324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乳壓電腦清主機板　女工程師拍灰塵網友暴動","createTime":"2018-11-17T04:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T13:23:51.000Z","uid":72009,"like":133,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"022aeeee0db50baf055246b5ba6eae5714a01bf5","tid":905324,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"身為工程師的小嗨，應Davio拜託，前來幫忙檢查電腦變慢問題，只見小嗨忽站忽蹲地擦拭主機板，一邊解釋速度變慢原因，但呼之欲出的上圍實在太引人注目，幫觀眾謀福利的Davio，當然不能辜負眾人期望，問了小嗨「所以妳等一下要清（親）哪裡？」、「臉頰嗎？」，豈料更犯規的還在後頭，秉持「要清就清滿」的精神，小嗨把雙峰直接壓在主機上，卻讓自己的棉質白色小可愛沾滿灰塵，惹得她驚呼「太灰了吧！」，隨手就朝車頭燈撥去，想不到這一撥，可撥得網友春心蕩漾，陣陣乳波逼網友直尖叫「我心跳直接突破天際」。<br />\n隨後小嗨還貼心地更換記憶體，但網友早就不在乎修電腦的進度，除了留言區瞬間湧入大群「我家電腦也壞掉」的人，更頓時暴動「可惡...害我重複看很多次 」、「記憶體真的好大好大」、「我沒有看到電腦呀？！ 」、「我也想被小嗨清一下」、「為什麼這部影片會一直自動回放」、「拍衣服灰塵那段，我跳針了兩個小時」。（影創中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181117/1467737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181117%2F1467737&d=s3MI7VAOkm5bhBhmo8PddJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5ecf9898\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20181117%2F1467737&h=3a1e69e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20181117/1467737</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181117/640_1704888fa0bb0cdeceb63667842b2728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181117%2F640_1704888fa0bb0cdeceb63667842b2728.jpg&h=64d5ce86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181117/640_99f3980eca39c813b309c75d35496286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181117%2F640_99f3980eca39c813b309c75d35496286.jpg&h=455ef44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f973050feea79c1379187f260fc2104f